---

<Layout>
	<main>
		<div id="about">
			<div id="basic_info">
				<h1 id="name">
					Quinn
					<br>
					<span id="last_name">Merkel</span>
				</h1>

				<p id="contact_info">
					Student <br>
					North Carolina State University <br>
					Computer Science Engineering; Cybersecurity Focus <br>
					<a href="mailto:qemerkel@ncsu.edu">qemerkel@ncsu.edu</a> <br>
					<a href="mailto:quinnmerkel@gmail.com">quinnmerkel@gmail.com</a> <br>
					Github: <a href="https://github.com/qmerkel10305">github.com/qmerkel10305</a> <br>
				</p>
			</div>
			<img id="profile_img" src={merkelImg.src} alt="Profile Picture">
		</div>
		<p>
			I am a Student at NC State, studying for a degree in Computer Science Engineering, focusing in Cybersecurity. I am a member of the <a href="https://aerialroboticsclub.com" target="_blank">Aerial Robotics Club</a>, and am currently serving as its Software Subteam Lead. As a member of ARC, I have designed backend systems for taking, processing, storing, and displaying images taken by our drone. In addition, I have served as Webmaster, and during that time used the HUGO framework to update and maintain the club's website. 
		</p>
		
		<!-- Internships and Research -->
		<section id="internship_research">
			<h1>
				Internship & Research Interest
			</h2>

			<p>
				I am currently a Junior, expecting to graduate in Spring of 2027. I am looking for any internship or research opportunities related to Cybersecurity. I have experience with Java, Python, and C, as well as penetration testing, web development, and network security through classes, clubs, and personal projects. 
			</p>
		</section>

		<!-- Skills -->
		<section id="skills">
			<h1>Skills</h1>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Programming Languages:</strong> 
					<ul>
						<li>Java</li>
						<li>Python</li>
						<li>C</li>
					</ul>
				<li><strong>Web Development:</strong></li>
					<ul>
						<li>HTML</li>
						<li>CSS</li>
						<li>HUGO</li>
						<li>Astro</li>
						<li>Server hosting, specifically Caddy</li>
						<li>FastAPI / Python backend scripting</li>
					</ul>
				<li><strong>Cybersecurity:</strong></li>
					<ul>
						<li>Penetration Testing</li>
						<li>Network Security</li>
					</ul>
				<li><strong>Version Control:</strong></li>
					<ul>
						<li>Git / Github</li>
					</ul>
				<li><strong>Other:</strong></li>
					<ul>
						<li>Linux</li>
						<li>Docker</li>
					</ul>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<!-- Projects -->
		<section id="projects">
			<h1>Projects</h1>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<strong>ARC Drone Imaging System:</strong> Designed backend systems for image collection, processing, and display for the Aerial Robotics Club.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>ARC Website:</strong> Maintained and updated club website using HUGO framework.
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<!-- Contact Info -->
		<section id="contact">
			<h1>
				Contact Me
			</h1>

			<p>
				Primary Email: <a href="mailto:quinnmerkel@gmail.com">quinnmerkel@gmail.com</a> <br>
				School Email: <a href="mailto:qemerkel@ncsu.edu">qemerkel@ncsu.edu</a> <br>
				<a href="https://github.com/qmerkel10305">Github</a> <br>
				<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/quinn-merkel/">LinkedIn</a> <br>
